results.lead_paragraph: While Yves Saint Laurent pre-dates the "Project Runway" generation's love affair with fashion TV, there's still plenty of YouTube treasures that capture his immense creativity and Gallic wit. First up, a vintage clip from a mysterious French documentary on the designer. Beside the candy-colored knits, the best part of the snippet is Saint Laurent's own musings, a translation of which appears below.

results.abstract: International Space Station's single toilet is fixed with replacement pump delivered by shuttle Discovery (S)

headline.main: Space Station Toilet Is Working Again

results.snippet: The troublesome toilet appears to be working again, thanks to a replacement pump taken to the station by the shuttle Discovery.
results.lead_paragraph: The troublesome toilet aboard the International Space Station appears to be working again, thanks to a replacement pump taken to the station by the shuttle Discovery. ''The toilet appears to have been repaired,'' said Rob Navias, the commentator for the National Aeronautics and Space Administration's video channel on the Web, NASA TV (www.nasa.gov/multimedia/nasatv/).
